<TEXT>
NOW IS a good time to invest in German bonds, according to Mr Ulrich Ramm,
executive vice-president in charge of analysis and corporate communications
at Commerzbank AG in Frankfurt. Equities will depend more on a satisfactory
outcome to this year's difficult wage round.
