<TEXT>
POLYFINANCE, the French laundry and sports equipment distributor, plans to
move into the UK via a recommended cash offer for its former parent,
Polymark International, the industrial laundry and label manufacturer and
supplier.
Polyfinance, which was set up as a separate company in 1990 following a
management buy-out, is offering 37p and 164 1/2 p respectively for each
